    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>basa fillets</strong> into thin strips, then add them to a bowl with the <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin </strong>and the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up, then put in the fridge to marinate until later</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
