          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> as finely as you can</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced red onion</strong> and cook for 6 min or until softened</p>",
